Things to enable/do manually

###########
# hidepid #
###########
Add the following to /etc/fstab:

# hidepid
proc	/proc	proc	nosuid,nodev,noexec,hidepid=2,gid=proc	0	0

##########################
# System Services/Timers #
##########################
Mask:
systemd-ask-password-console.path
systemd-ask-password-wall.path
udisks2.service

Enable:
apparmor.service
auditd.service
bluetooth.service
dictd.service
firewalld.service
NetworkManager.service
rngd.service
tlp.service
paccache.timer
undervolt.timer

########################
# User Services/Timers #
########################
Mask:
at-spi-dbus-bus.service
gvfs-daemon.service
gvfs-metadata.service
gvfs-udisks2-volume-monitor.service
gpg-agent-browser.socket
gpg-agent-extra.socket
gpg-agent-ssh.socket

Enable:
foot-server.service
gpg-agent.service
mako.service
ssh-agent.service
swaybg.service
swayidle.service
syncthing.service
waybar.service
wlsunset.service
wob.service
cache_unread_emails.timer
mbsync.timer
vdirsyncer.timer

#############
# firewalld #
#############
firewall-cmd --set-default-zone=drop
firewall-cmd --add-service=syncthing
firewall-cmd --runtime-to-permanent

#################
# Miscellaneous #
#################
Make the following dirs in ~/.config:
Code - OSS/User
micro
transmission-daemon
systemd/user

Make ~/.local/share/mail with the following subdirs:
dev-krathalan
hunter-krathalan
school-gmail
school-krathalan
shopping-krathalan

Ensure Xorg is running rootless.
Use booster, set up secure boot.
Copy fox.sh to /usr/bin and chown root:root.
Run `vdirsyncer discover contacts`.
Set up vscode with Material Theme, Material Theme Icons, and Shellcheck extensions.
Set up ~/.local/share/chromium-extensions.
